   <head>To his worthy friend Microphilus.</head>
   <l>HOw should one blaze the worth of little things?</l>
   <l>Thus; th'are as sparkling Di<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>amonds to rings:</l>
   <l>But what needs praise from a<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ny, since thy pen</l>
   <l>Hath prov'd a Dwarfe the mi<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>racle of men.</l>
   <signed>D. L.</signed>
